{"tid":1427071,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[警告] 機場集會務必保持和平","createTime":"2019-08-07T04:51:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T09:01:14.000Z","uid":108305,"like":89,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"53849888a8621daef4de322e7a122deaae963407","tid":1427071,"uid":108305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:51:57.000Z","msg":"上星期五既和平集會已帶黎極大國際性迴響<br />\n現階段只需擴大人數 保持和平<br />\n任何衝擊 eg禁區 唔會帶到任何效果 連報仇都講唔上<br />\n罪名都會更為嚴重<br />\n而家睇禁區既係海關同移記<br />\n係我地兩大盟友<br />\n所以切勿作出任何衝擊"},{"pid":"d59da5b66962cde36eab551879a99e3859e07de0","tid":1427071,"uid":108305,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:52:51.000Z","msg":"切勿衝擊"},{"pid":"108cb0c5bf6ee93b10e8f35f49ba55929a2f0252","tid":1427071,"uid":298428,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:58:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">仲要防止上次果個阿伯事件<br />\n<br />\n提防老臨做戲 挑撥 激怒在場人士<br />\n<br />\n要搵人拍野MON住全場全過程<br />\n<br />\n有事都有片為証</span></span>"},{"pid":"1c501bdb276e4a9c02ac51e0bdd9079c7d084290","tid":1427071,"uid":108305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:07:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b43a37e3491882e1b4af4b022e85f1e7e71d0dc4","tid":1427071,"uid":108305,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:08:54.000Z","msg":"切勿被三毛道德綁架<br />\n做傻事都要盲撐不割蓆<br />\n不割蓆既意思同一陣線<br />\n而同一陣線就更加要制止極不合理既行為<br />\n不斷進諫<br />\n而不是睇住佢地死"},{"pid":"dde29b22e3e858aa5ce6fa51f91e57c398259861","tid":1427071,"uid":4727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:09:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d7d15e9dc7836c4c8f10311e530dc848fee6b9e9","tid":1427071,"uid":108305,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:10:43.000Z","msg":"衝禁區=攻打老解軍營<br />\n切勿聽三毛吹風<br />\n佢地推緊人死"},{"pid":"ce9bb59b4f3f1188150518d8b4bef3c22cd172ff","tid":1427071,"uid":108305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:11:53.